    "The reason behind the improved performance of BCNN-CWS is that BCNN adopts a CNN as the basic architecture and uses dilation convolution operation to limit the number of convolution layers.",
    "Moreover, because BCNN and IDCNN are based on the same basic architecture, the running time of them is about the same.",
